name: Aritzia Report - Pick Location Utilization
command:
/*Location Summary*/
[SELECT bin_type,
        COUNT(bin_type) locations,
        is(SUM(CASE WHEN locsts IN ('F', 'P') THEN 1
                   END), 0) AS used,
        is(SUM(CASE WHEN ab.pndqvl > 0 AND locsts = 'E' THEN 1
                   END), 0) AS pending,
        COUNT(bin_type) - is(SUM(CASE WHEN locsts IN ('F', 'P') THEN 1
                                     END), 0) - is(SUM(CASE WHEN ab.pndqvl > 0 AND locsts = 'E' THEN 1
                                                           END), 0) as available,
        is(SUM(CASE WHEN locsts = 'I' THEN 1
                   END), 0) AS error
   FROM (SELECT CASE WHEN lc.maxqvl >= 92000 THEN 'BULK'
                     WHEN lc.maxqvl >= 14000 THEN 'XL'
                     WHEN lc.maxqvl >= 6400 THEN 'L'
                     WHEN lc.maxqvl >= 3500 THEN 'M'
                     WHEN lc.maxqvl >= 2400 THEN 'S'
                     WHEN lc.maxqvl >= 2399 THEN '5S'
                     WHEN lc.maxqvl < 2399 THEN 'XS'
                END AS bin_type,
                lc.stoloc,
                lc.pndqvl,
                qv.prtnum,
                lc.pckflg,
                lc.stoflg,
                lc.repflg,
                lc.locsts
           FROM locmst lc
           LEFT
           JOIN qvlwrk qv
             ON qv.stoloc = lc.stoloc
          WHERE lc.arecod = 'PICK'
            and lc.useflg = 1) ab
  GROUP BY bin_type] >> res
|
if (@? = 0)
{
    list warehouses
    |
    expand environment variable
     where name = '$' || @wh_id || 'outputs' || '\Pick Location Utilization'
    |
    publish data
     where path = @value
    |
    write csv file
     where resdata = @res
       and filnam = 'pck_loc_utilization-' || to_char(sysdate, 'YYYYMMDD-hh24mi') || '.csv '
       and path = @path
}
